---
title: Argentinian-Style Steaks with Chimichurri Aioli, Potatoes and Salad
description: Tonight we're giving classic Argentinian-style steak a twist with creamy chimichurri, and we might just make you fall in love. Fresh herbs and garlic are mixed with mayo, vinegar and Dijon to create an irresistible dipper for your steak and potatoes. This beauty is guaranteed to pick you up at the end of a long day!
